{"article_id":"5HLFuk2VaFZQ9iJ3","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Today is the deadline","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"for most Americans","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"to have ObamaCare insurance","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"beginning Jan. 1 ,","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"but a series of administration fixes and delays is turning the milestone into a day","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"that for many Americans will underscore the uncertainty about the future of the law .","depth":5},{"id":6,"text":"The original plan was simple","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"-- that Americans","depth":9},{"id":8,"text":"who enrolled in ObamaCare , online or otherwise , by Dec. 23","depth":10},{"id":9,"text":"and paid in full","depth":10},{"id":10,"text":"would have insurance","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"when coverage kicks in New Year ' s Day .","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"But the disastrous Oct. 1 start for the federal website and some state-run sites","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"-- marked by crashes and the dissemination of incorrect information --","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"sent President Obama and other top administration officials scrambling to change the law in hopes","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"of bolstering enrollment numbers .","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"The president has expressed confidence over the past several days","depth":6},{"id":17,"text":"that the changes have helped .","depth":6},{"id":18,"text":"On Sunday , he restated his case","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"that ObamaCare is on the right track","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"but urged those","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"who had yet to enroll","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"to do so by Monday .","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"\" The law is working , \"","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"he said in a statement .","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"\" If you don ' t have health insurance ,","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"go to [ the site ] right now","depth":11},{"id":27,"text":"and sign up .","depth":11},{"id":28,"text":"If you do it before December 23rd ,","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"you can be covered on the first day of the New Year .","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"... I ' m asking you to spread the word","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"about getting covered . \"","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"Among the first changes for individual insurance was the president ' s proposed legislative fix in mid-November , amid the issuing of millions of insurance cancellation notices .","depth":3},{"id":33,"text":"Obama gave insurers the option","depth":6},{"id":34,"text":"to extend plans to customers for an extra year ,","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"even if the plans failed to meet ObamaCare standards .","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"`` I completely get how upsetting this can be for a lot of Americans , ''","depth":7},{"id":37,"text":"the president said at the time .","depth":7},{"id":38,"text":"`` Americans","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"whose plans have been canceled","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"can choose to enroll in the same kind of plan . ''","depth":7},{"id":41,"text":"However , the move drew sharp criticism from congressional Republicans and other ObamaCare critics .","depth":5},{"id":42,"text":"`` There is no way","depth":8},{"id":43,"text":"to fix this , ''","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"House Speaker John Boehner said .","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"`` I am highly skeptical","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"they can do this administratively . ''","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"Last week , administration officials appealed again to insurers ,","depth":4},{"id":48,"text":"asking them to accept partial payments or backdate policies for those","depth":6},{"id":49,"text":"who enroll after Monday","depth":6},{"id":50,"text":"-- in hopes","depth":6},{"id":51,"text":"that more Americans , not less , would have insurance by Jan. 1 .","depth":6},{"id":52,"text":"They also said","depth":4},{"id":53,"text":"the estimated 500,000","depth":7},{"id":54,"text":"who had yet to replace cancelled policies","depth":7},{"id":55,"text":"could get bare-bones ones","depth":6},{"id":56,"text":"and that roughly 3.9 million lower-income Americans have qualified for ObamaCare through the law 's Medicaid expansion","depth":6},{"id":57,"text":"-- collectively closing the enrollment gap","depth":7},{"id":58,"text":"created by the estimated 4 million to 5 million cancellations .","depth":7},{"id":59,"text":"The president said Friday","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"that 1 million Americans through the third week in December had enrolled in ObamaCare .","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"It was a sharp increase","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"compared to the mere 365,000","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"who had enrolled through November 30","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"and signaled","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"that many of the computer glitches had been fixed .","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"But the number remains far short of the 3.3 million","depth":8},{"id":67,"text":"the administration had hoped for prior to the October rollout .","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"Still , several underlying problems persist ,","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"including the accuracy of the numbers","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"and how many of those enrolled have in fact paid for their policies .","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"Such problems could create far more serious consequences in the coming weeks","depth":8},{"id":72,"text":"should people","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"who think","depth":11},{"id":74,"text":"they have insurance under ObamaCare","depth":11},{"id":75,"text":"go to a pharmacy or doctor ' s office","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"and find out otherwise .","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"In addition , the complexity of the law ,","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"including who is exempt from what ,","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"will continue to confuse Americans ,","depth":8},{"id":80,"text":"Robert Moffit , director of The Heritage Foundation 's Center for Health Policy Studies , told FoxNews.com on Friday .","depth":7},{"id":81,"text":"\" This whole thing has turned into a rat ' s nest of rules and regulations , \"","depth":8},{"id":82,"text":"he said .","depth":8},{"id":83,"text":"\" Who would have thought","depth":9},{"id":84,"text":"Health and Human Services Secretary Kathleen Sebelius would grant so many hardships ? ...","depth":9},{"id":85,"text":"This administration is under the mindset","depth":9},{"id":86,"text":"of how America is supposed to work ,","depth":10},{"id":87,"text":"which has nothing to do with how it really works . \"","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"The White House ' s ultimate goal is to provide insurance for an estimate 30 million Americans ,","depth":7},{"id":89,"text":"which includes subsidizing costs for low-income individuals .","depth":7},{"id":90,"text":"The deadline","depth":8},{"id":91,"text":"to enroll","depth":9},{"id":92,"text":"without facing a tax penalty","depth":9},{"id":93,"text":"is March 31 .","depth":7},{"id":94,"text":"Capitol Hill Republicans and other ObamaCare critics have tried numerous times to \" defund \" or replace the law ,","depth":6},{"id":95,"text":"with the GOP-led House holding at least 40 votes on the issue .","depth":6},{"id":96,"text":"What Congress and Obama will do","depth":6},{"id":97,"text":"when they return to Washington","depth":6},{"id":98,"text":"remains unclear .","depth":5},{"id":99,"text":"The president is committed to getting insurance for the roughly 20 percent of Americans","depth":8},{"id":100,"text":"who previously didn ' t have coverage ,","depth":8},{"id":101,"text":"too be sure .","depth":7},{"id":102,"text":"\" Things will get better , \"","depth":8},{"id":103,"text":"he said last month .","depth":8},{"id":104,"text":"\" I make no apologies","depth":9},{"id":105,"text":"for us taking this on","depth":9},{"id":106,"text":"because somebody , sooner or later , had to do it . \"","depth":8},{"id":107,"text":"However , Moffit and others think","depth":6},{"id":108,"text":"the president might be forced to except changes from Capitol Hill","depth":7},{"id":109,"text":"as Democrats","depth":9},{"id":110,"text":"seeking re-election in 2014","depth":9},{"id":111,"text":"need to show voters","depth":9},{"id":112,"text":"they can and have fixed the problems .","depth":9}],"relations":[{"parent":225,"left":159,"right":224,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":159,"left":144,"right":158,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":144,"left":118,"right":143,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":118,"left":116,"right":117,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":116,"left":115,"right":3,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":115,"left":0,"right":114,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":114,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":117,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":143,"left":127,"right":142,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":127,"left":123,"right":126,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":123,"left":6,"right":122,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":122,"left":121,"right":11,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":121,"left":120,"right":10,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":120,"left":7,"right":119,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":119,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":126,"left":124,"right":125,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":124,"left":12,"right":13,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":125,"left":14,"right":15,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":142,"left":128,"right":141,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":128,"left":16,"right":17,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":141,"left":132,"right":140,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":132,"left":129,"right":131,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":129,"left":18,"right":19,"relation":"elaboration